edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.examples
Class BitstreamDiff

java.lang.Object
  edu.byu.ece.rapidSmith.bitstreamTools.examples.BitstreamDiff

public class BitstreamDiff
extends java.lang.Object

This executable loads two bitstreams and determines the differences. It also contains a number of static methods that can be used within beanshell scripts or other executables. TODO: - Provide ability to check differences between the headers or not (it currently ignores this)
